import React from "react";

const BellIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="43"
      height="43"
      viewBox="0 0 43 43"
    >
      <g id="Groupe_11" data-name="Groupe 11" transform="translate(-94 -176)">
        <rect
          id="Rectangle_12"
          data-name="Rectangle 12"
          width="43"
          height="43"
          transform="translate(94 176)"
          fill="rgba(255,255,255,0)"
        />
        <g
          id="Icon_feather-bell"
          data-name="Icon feather-bell"
          transform="translate(104.241 186.992)"
        >
          <path
            id="Tracé_10"
            data-name="Tracé 10"
            d="M16.269,7.707a4.707,4.707,0,1,0-9.415,0c0,5.492-2.354,7.061-2.354,7.061H18.622S16.269,13.2,16.269,7.707"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.5"
          />
          <path
            id="Tracé_11"
            data-name="Tracé 11"
            d="M18.12,31.5a1.569,1.569,0,0,1-2.715,0"
            transform="translate(-5.201 -13.593)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.5"
          />
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default BellIcon;
